description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 93, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 279, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, Leverage for East, Leverage for South, and 5 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10933-56650-2.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [279 Votes, Hall of Fame]
